                    <span>A solid insight into the important linkage between XML and Data Architecture. The author's approach and recommendations on reusable data structures outline the path to enabling structural consistency and standards conformity. I work in Data Architecture and this book supports the viable dependency XML and Data Architecture have on one another. This is a book I highly recommend to all XML and architecture practitioners.</span>
                  
